duck: "Guaranteed" (Eddie Vedder song) - "Guaranteed" is a song written and performed by Pearl Jam vocalist Eddie Vedder from the Into the Wild soundtrack (2007).
Guaranteed (Ronnie Drew album) - Guaranteed is Ronnie Drew's second solo album that was released in 1978 and produced by Pete St. John, who wrote many of the featured tracks.
Guaranteed (Level 42 album) - Guaranteed is the ninth studio album by the British musical group Level 42, released in 1991, their first album of the 1990s.
guaranteed definition: to undertake to answer for the debt, default, or miscarriage of.
Guaranteed (Phatfish album) - Guaranteed is the 2007 studio album from Phatfish.
"Guaranteed" (Level 42 song) - "Guaranteed" is a song by English musical group Level 42.
Guaranteed (Morris Day album) - Guaranteed, released in 1992, is the third solo album by R&B singer Morris Day.
